description: This Blue Bunny Insignia is a thank you to our wonderful holders to celebrate our [2 year anniversary](https://twitter.com/uwucrewnft/status/1699120216125342052)! Our adventure together has been absolutely incredible. Thank you so much to everyone who has supported us!!! This Insignia grants you access to 2 dressing room items: Blue Bunny Dress (Outfit) and Blue Bunny Bow (Hat)!
